title: Introduction to Computer Architecture
description: Introduction to computer architecture. Computer system design. Processor design. Control design. Memory systems. Two units of credit offered for CSE 141 if CSE 142 taken previously. Prerequisites: CSE 30 or ECE 30 and CSE 140; restricted to CS25, CS26, CS27, CS29, and EC26 majors. All other students will be allowed as space permits.
